# Deprecated Patterns

## Avoid Using
- Deprecated lifecycle methods in React components.
- Inline styles directly in JSX.

## Use Instead
- Use React hooks for managing component state and lifecycle.
- Utilize styled-components or a similar library for styling.

## Strong Emphasis
- Ensure all deprecated patterns are clearly marked and provide the correct, up-to-date patterns with clear instructions.
